*{{flag|Liberia}}: Minister of Information [http://www.micat.gov.lr/index.php]
*{{flag|Malawi}}: Minister of Information, Communication and Tourism [http://www.malawi.gov.mw/information1/index.info.htm]
*{{flag|Namibia}}: [[Cabinet of Namibia|Minister of Information and Communication Technology]]
*{{flag|Nepal}}: Minister of Information and Communications [http://www.moic.gov.np/]
*{{flag|Nigeria}}: [[Government of Nigeria|Minister of Information and Communications]] [http://www.nigeria.gov.ng/]
*{{flag|Norway}}: [[Norwegian Ministry of Culture and Enlightenment|Ministry of Culture and Enlightenment]] - (A historical position in the Norwegian government during the German occupation during [[World War Two]])
