*{{flag|Russia}}: [[List of Ministers of National Enlightenment|Minister of National Enlightenment]] - (A historical position in [[Imperial Russia]] before the 1917 [[October Revolution]])
*{{flag|Rhodesia}}: Minister of Information, Immigration and Tourism - (A historical position in [[Rhodesia]] during [[Unilateral Declaration of Independence (Rhodesia)|UDI]])
*{{flag|Saudi Arabia}}: Minister of Culture and Information [http://www.saudinf.com/main/c6e.htm]
*{{flag|Singapore}}: [[Ministry of Information, Communications and the Arts|Minister of Information, Communications and the Arts]] [http://app.mica.gov.sg/]
