*{{flag|Zimbabwe}}: Minister of Information and Publicity  [http://www.gta.gov.zw/ministries/ministries%20.htm]
*{{UK}}: [[Ministry of Information (United_Kingdom)|Ministry of Information]] - (A historical position in the [[United Kingdom|British]] [[government]] during the [[World War I|First]] and [[World War II|Second World War]]s as head of the Ministry of Information)
